A vast underground cavern filled with towering crystalline data storage structures, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures and warm amber lighting. Massive translucent crystal formations glow from within, each containing swirling streams of tiny glowing particles representing stored messages. A small figure in a maintenance jumpsuit stands on a floating platform, dwarfed by the enormous storage crystals that stretch endlessly into misty depths. Delicate mechanical pipes and brass fixtures connect the crystals in an organic network. Dust motes float through shafts of golden light streaming from openings far above. The atmosphere feels both magical and industrial, suggesting infinite capacity yet careful stewardship of precious digital memories.
